Gina Palerme https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gina_Palerme 0 . Gina Palerme (1885-1977) born Irene de Maulmont was a French actress and dancer. Palerme appeared on the stage in London in November 1910 and played in several well-known London houses up to 1919. She also appeared in about a dozen French titled silent films from 1921 through 1925. She died in France in December 1977. .
